high_descs: Turn left and walk to the bathroom sink on the left.
Pick up the red rag in the sink.
Turn around, step forward and turn around to face the vanity.
Open the right side drawer, place the rag in the lower left corner, close the drawer.
Turn around, step forward, then turn left to see a red rag on the bath tub.
Pick up the red rag on the edge of the bath tub.
Return to the bathroom vanity drawers.
Open the draw, place the rag on top of the other rag, close the draw.
anns.task_desc: Place two rags inside the vanity drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the front of the sink to your left.
Remove the rag from the sink.
Move over to the right side of the sink.
Place the rag in the drawer, under the right side of the sink.
Turn to the bath tub on your right.
Take the rag out of the bath tub.
Turn back to the right side of the sink.
Place the rag inside the drawer, under the right side of the sink, on top of the other rag.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags in the bathroom drawer.

high_descs: walk to the front of the sink
take the red cloth from the sink
take the cloth to the right side of the sink
put the cloth in the top drawer on the right
go to the tub basin
pick up the red cloth from the basin
take the cloth to the drawer by the sink
put the cloth in the drawer
anns.task_desc: put two red clothes in a drawer under the counter to the right of the sink
